{"text_id":166203,"tokens":["In"," this"," work",","," we"," address"," the"," challenge"," of"," achieving"," high"," spectral"," efficiency"," and"," high"," diversity"," order"," in"," cooperative"," transmission"," protocols","."," Traditional"," cooperative"," communication"," systems"," often"," face"," a"," trade","-","off"," between"," spectral"," efficiency"," and"," diversity"," gain",","," limiting"," their"," performance"," in"," multi","user"," environments","."," Our"," research"," is"," motivated"," by"," the"," need"," to"," enhance"," the"," reliability"," and"," throughput"," of"," wireless"," networks",","," particularly"," in"," scenarios"," with"," multiple"," users"," and"," varying"," channel"," conditions","."," We"," propose"," a"," novel"," approach"," that"," integrates"," multi","user"," detection"," (","MUD",")"," and"," network"," coding"," (","NC",")"," to"," optimize"," the"," performance"," of"," cooperative"," transmission"," protocols","."," By"," leveraging"," MUD",","," we"," effectively"," mitigate"," interference"," and"," enhance"," signal"," detection"," accuracy",","," while"," NC"," enables"," efficient"," data"," transmission"," and"," error"," correction","."," Our"," proposed"," protocol"," demonstrates"," significant"," improvements"," in"," both"," spectral"," efficiency"," and"," diversity"," order"," compared"," to"," conventional"," methods","."," Through"," extensive"," simulations",","," we"," validate"," the"," effectiveness"," of"," our"," approach",","," showing"," that"," it"," achieves"," superior"," performance"," in"," terms"," of"," bit"," error"," rate"," (","BER",")"," and"," throughput","."," The"," results"," indicate"," that"," our"," protocol"," can"," substantially"," enhance"," the"," robustness"," and"," efficiency"," of"," wireless"," communication"," systems",","," making"," it"," a"," promising"," solution"," for"," future"," network"," deployments","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt4o","la